title: Looking for a good "up to date" jungling guide
body: Been away for ages, inevitably the jungle has changed a bit... just wondered if anyone either has some basic advice for jungle clear routes or can point me in the direction of a half decent guide? Thanks.

replies.body: If you give me a list of champs you will be playing or if you need help making a list of junglers I  can help you but I'm only in b1 although I have decent game knowledge and experience in the jungle
